title: WTF | Photo: Is this the greatest Irish fan photo from the Rugby World Cup so far?
text:
We think it's safe to say this little girl was heavily invested in the Ireland versus France match on Sunday.
That or she happened to stand on some LEGO at the same time that Conor Murray scored a try for Ireland. We like to think it's the former.
Via 9GAG
